Aston Villa beat Liverpool 2-1 in the FA Cup semi-final at Wembley on Sunday . 
  Jack Grealish is a fan of the club and his father Kevin has bought season tickets for his sons since they were born . 
  The 19-year-old wore his socks round his ankles in a tribute to George Best . 
  He has to buy kid-sized shinpads to meet safety regulations . 
  Aston Villa face Manchester United in the final on Saturday . 
 